    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――年始特番の二週間前",
      "startTime": 0,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_bicycle-01.m4a",
          "delay": 1439.9999857,
          "startTime": 1.4399999857
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_10_01-rui001.m4a",
      "text": "はぁ……はぁ……ラストスパート……！\n……ふぅ、これで今日のトレーニングは終わりね",
      "startTime": 7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_10_01-rui002.m4a",
      "text": "え、{user}さん？　いつからそこに？\nすみません、集中していて気付かなくて",
      "startTime": 15.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_10_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "フィットネスバイク、お疲れ様\n朝から漕いでたけど、まさかずっと漕いでいたのか？",
      "startTime": 21.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_10_01-rui003.m4a",
      "text": "途中で一度、休憩しました\nでも『挑戦』の本番では、休憩なんて出来ませんから",
      "startTime": 28.5999993642,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_10_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "二週間後の、新年の特番でやる『挑戦』企画か……\n瑠依は、人力飛行機で飛ぶんだよな",
      "startTime": 37.7333326976,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_10_01-rui004.m4a",
      "text": "そうです、失敗する訳にはいきませんから\nそれに、本番では空で漕ぐんです",
      "startTime": 44.2666660309,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_10_01-rui005.m4a",
      "text": "天候や風向きだって影響するでしょうし\n練習とは、全然違うはずですから……",
      "startTime": 50.5666660309,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_10_01-rui006.m4a",
      "text": "だから練習では、本番の何倍も漕げるように\n鍛えておきたいんです",
      "startTime": 57.2999993642,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_hungry-01.m4a",
          "delay": 5526.666666700003,
          "startTime": 62.8266660309
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_10_01-rui007.m4a",
      "text": "丸一日、トレーニングに専念出来るのは\n今日が最後ですし――",
      "startTime": 61.7333326976,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_10_01-rui008.m4a",
      "text": "あ……お、お腹の音が、こんなに大きく鳴るなんて……\n……すみません、お昼ご飯、食べ忘れてました",
      "startTime": 69.9333291371,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_10_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "ちゃんと食べないと力が出ないぞ\n良かったら、一緒に昼飯にしないか？",
      "startTime": 77.2343475669,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_10_01-rui009.m4a",
      "text": "え、本当ですか？\nぜひご一緒したいです",
      "startTime": 82.0666599273,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_10_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "と言っても、この間トリエルが撮影したCMに出てきた\nカップ麺だけど……うどんとそば、どっちがいい？",
      "startTime": 87.7999958038,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_10_01-rui010.m4a",
      "text": "あぁ、スポンサーさんから差し入れが届いてましたね\nうーん……では私は、おうどんにします",
      "startTime": 97.1666624705,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_10_01-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "分かった、じゃあ俺はお湯を沸かしておくよ\n体を冷やすといけないし、着替えてくるといい",
      "startTime": 105.5333291371,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_10_01-rui011.m4a",
      "text": "昼食のご用意、ありがとうございます\nわぁ……お出汁のいい匂い……お腹ぺこぺこです",
      "startTime": 114.8858523108,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_10_01-rui012.m4a",
      "text": "私、カップ麺って初めて食べます。CMでは、お揚げを\n食べるシーンしかなくて。簡単に作れて便利ですね",
      "startTime": 125.3666624705,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_10_01-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "は、初めて？　驚いたな……。おっと、五分経ったな\n人生初のカップ麺、食べてみてくれ",
      "startTime": 137.0201961137,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_10_01-rui013.m4a",
      "text": "もう出来たんですか？　本当に早いんですね……！\nそれではいただきます。ふふ、CMでも食べたお揚げ",
      "startTime": 145.3999937693,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_10_01-rui014.m4a",
      "text": "ふー、ふー……ん～！　しっかり味が染みていますね\nおうどんもコシがあって、とっても美味しいです",
      "startTime": 160.3420492373,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_10_01-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "こっちのそばも、喉越しが良くてうまいぞ\n沢山いただいたから、今度、そばも食べてみてくれ",
      "startTime": 167.3999937693,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_10_01-rui015.m4a",
      "text": "ふぅ、ごちそうさまでした。……それにしても\n年末で慌ただしいはずなのに、事務所は静かですね",
      "startTime": 178.699996821,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_10_01-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "みんな仕事だから、事務所はかえって静かだよ\n瑠依は今日、ちょうどオフだったんだよな？",
      "startTime": 187.2666634876,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_10_01-rui016.m4a",
      "text": "はい、私は今日が年内最後のオフですね\n年末年始は大忙しです",
      "startTime": 194.3666634876,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_10_01-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "今年はまだ二週間も残ってるけど、本当に大丈夫か？\n瑠依の自己管理がしっかりしているのは、知ってるけど",
      "startTime": 201.6333301543,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_10_01-rui017.m4a",
      "text": "お気遣い、ありがとうございます\nでも、どうしても今は頑張りたくて",
      "startTime": 207.499996821,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_10_01-rui018.m4a",
      "text": "私がやる企画――『トリエルに翼を授けよう』は\nファンの想いを背負った『挑戦』です",
      "startTime": 215.2333301543,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_10_01-rui019.m4a",
      "text": "ファンの想いを乗せた飛行機で\n空を飛ぶんだと思うと、いつも以上に頑張りたくて",
      "startTime": 219.499996821,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_10_01-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "分かった。でもほどほどにな\n新年の本番までに、体を壊さないようにしてくれ",
      "startTime": 226.799996821,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_10_01-rui020.m4a",
      "text": "はい。新年の大型特番で司会をするのは、初めてですし\n万全の体調で本番に臨みます",
